=======================
= Java PapaBench Core =
=======================

This project provides a core for Java PapaBench which is independent on a target platform.
It contains a fly-by-wire and autopilot logic, runnable for tasks, implementation of PIDs.

Further, implementation also provides a simple simulator of flying environment following the ideas of Paparazzi simulator.


For further information, please, visit the project page:
http://d3s.mff.cuni.cz/~malohlava/projects/jpapabench/

